"""
TLM Graphene Simulation Package
================================

Transmission Line Matrix (TLM) simulation for graphene sheets
in the terahertz frequency range (0-10 THz).

Modules:
    - tlm_core: Core TLM functions (init, scatter, connect, boundary)
    - graphene_model: Drude model for graphene conductivity
    - simulation: Main simulation class
    - visualization: Plotting utilities

Example:
    >>> from src.simulation import GrapheneTLMSimulation
    >>> sim = GrapheneTLMSimulation(fermi_energy=0.4, relaxation_time=100e-15)
    >>> results = sim.run()
    >>> sim.plot_coefficients()
"""

